comment: Builder class for custom chat or call intent.

startWithChat.comment: The intent will be initialized to start a chat activity.

startWithAudioVideoCall.comment: Create Call Activity with audio video call capability.

startWithAudioCall.comment: Create Call Activity with audio call capability.

startWithAudioUpgradableCall.comment: Create Call Activity with audio call capability upgradable to video.

startFromJoinCallUrl.comment: Create Call Activity from a url.
